    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Мулкни юридик шахснинг устав фондига киритишга розилик аризаси</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза киритилаётган ташкилот номи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Аризачининг яшаш манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризачининг рўйхатдан ўтган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда пропискада турувчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#8}Аризачининг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#9}Аризачига паспорт берилган худуд номи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#10}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Ариза ёзилган ҳудуд номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Ариза тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> турмуш ўртоғим </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Аризачи турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> номига расмийлаштирилган, биргаликдаги никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Аризачининг яшаш манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг рўйхатдан ўтган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйни </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Давлат рўйхатидан ўтказган ташкилотнинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилган рақам</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан рўйхатга олинган «</span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Рўйхатга олинган ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">»нинг устав фондига киритишига ўз розилигимни бераман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Келгусида мазкур уй-жой бўйича ҳеч кимга ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> _____________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Имзо _________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
